job.title: BHEL Technician  Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 136 Posts
job.body:
Total Vacancies:136

Name of the post:

  • Technician, Graduate Apprentice

Description:

The Bharat Heavy Electrical Limited (BHEL)  issued a total of136 vacancies for the posts of Technician, Graduate Apprentice. The online application for these posts under BHEL shall start from 01.04.2021. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 14.04.2021. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for BHEL Notification 2021 :

  • Mode of application: Online
  • For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 01.04.2021
  • The Last date to apply online is 14.04.2021

Educational qualification:

  • You must have the diploma/degree in 10th, 12th, ITI, Diploma, any field, B.E to apply for the post of Technician, Graduate Apprentice 

Age limit criteria:

  • The minimum age required to apply is 18 Years
  • The maximum age required to apply is 27 Years
  • For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.

Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Technician, Graduate Apprentice is INR 8000-9000/month
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that BHEL issued this notification for which posts.

  • Technician Apprentice 70 Posts
  • Graduate Apprentice 66 Posts

How to apply for BHEL Notification 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of BHEL.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of Technician, Graduate Apprentice.
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.
